subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: No. 13-seeded Ohio flustered top-seeded North Carolina, but the Tar Heels won their 11th consecutive regional semifinal game, a streak that includes three national championship runs.
